title: SPY's Happy Hour—March 14th, 2014—with mmx and Rebecca Underdown
description: Rebecca Underdown, an acupuncturist, yoga instructor and owner of Veridatta Skin, visited SPY's Happy Hour to explain how passion and emotion combine to affect ego, judgment and qi. The resultant connection between Happiness and Health reflects the human ability to approach life with a happy disposition, thus ensuring less illness, disease and a longer life while we pursue our true nature.
